About this item

  • Product Compatible - Only Compatible with Nintendo Wii and Wii U, the USB wired infrared sensor bar for Nintendo Wii, Wii U Consoles. When using the computer to run the emulator, please make sure to have bluetooth receptors (Computer built-in or additional equipment) for recognizing the remote.
  • Perfect Design - Durable quality material for perfect accuracy and long service life. Ergonomically designed for a simple and elegant appearance. Make your everyday video gaming convenient with its simplified operation.
  • Simple and Portable - Includes stand with adhesive for easy attachment to TV, monitor or any smooth surface. Come with a holder, easily attachment to TV, monitor. You can place the sensor above the TV or below the TV.
  • Easy to Use - Plug and play, perfect replacement or extra sensor for Wii or Wii U Consoles, works just like the original sensor bar, but powered by USB port.
  • Perfect Replacement - Our compatible sensor bar can be used with Nintendo Wii and Wii U consoles, it is a great replacement if your original sensor bar is lost, broken.

    Features:
    - Designed Fit for Wii consoles receiving the signal, perfect replacement for sensor bar.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
